{"tid":2362261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新變種武肺襲日 異於英國南非","createTime":"2021-01-11T10:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"569471c8ee7f2701824bddc7b75a7913b75dc6b8","tid":2362261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210111/UDDRD6UG2NABPCROAX7DAL2LBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210111%2FUDDRD6UG2NABPCROAX7DAL2LBQ%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2bf3b3fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210111%2FUDDRD6UG2NABPCROAX7DAL2LBQ%2F&h=5dd7e600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210111/UDDRD6UG2NABPCROAX7DAL2LBQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新變種武肺襲日 異於英國南非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vlpp3tVYEc0MOCW4ccIhOTp0Was=/1673x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNP6Z7CUPZCV5FABM2W5ZQROSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVlpp3tVYEc0MOCW4ccIhOTp0Was%3D%2F1673x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNP6Z7CUPZCV5FABM2W5ZQROSQ.jpg&h=dea64344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本東京都政府職員在鬧市一字排開，以標語牌呼籲市民回家避疫。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n日本政府厚生勞動省昨日表示，有四名從巴西抵達日本、確診武漢肺炎的旅客，被驗出一種不同於英國與南非變種病毒的全新武肺變種病毒。<br />\n<br />\n時事通信社報道，目前仍不清楚新變種病毒的傳染力、感染後病情嚴重程度，以及對疫苗有效性影響等，日本國立傳染病研究所等單位，正在進行詳細調查。報道指，這種新變種病毒，跟在英國與南非被發現的變種病毒有相同的變異之處，不過是另外一種新的變種病毒。<br />\n<br />\n厚生勞動省表示，這。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英女皇與皇夫已接種疫苗<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國白金漢宮前日公佈，94歲英女皇伊利沙伯二世與99歲皇夫菲臘親王當日已接種武漢肺炎疫苗。英國至今已有逾100萬人注射疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n女皇與皇夫屬於第二優先群組，即80歲或以上長者。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據報政府內部曾討論如何利用公眾人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"52e326a754386570d9c6a8d64faa61a3ada29c2a","tid":2362261,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"冇了冇了"},{"pid":"41af9b03298a40ea1bbb3b7c1e654f5fee3a5679","tid":2362261,"uid":192823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"幾時封日本關"},{"pid":"4ac9e8ee68d345853f994af29f3476ebf7101191","tid":2362261,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"支那仲要放幾多種毒出黎搞亂個世界<br />\n一日不滅支那，一日天下不歸仁"},{"pid":"24aace5c5807cbee8a525617540334e1286c37f7","tid":2362261,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"日本玩撚完"},{"pid":"53aae4f93f3b9c91d153e12834f34202fe182b9c","tid":2362261,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"日日變種一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快疫苗都唔會有用"}]}